pa Italiana]]</ref>||0||39||2\n|-\n|[[2006\u201307 Inter Milan season|2006\u201307]]\n|28||10||2||0||6<ref group=\"lower-alpha\" name=\"UCL\"/>||0||1<ref group=\"lower-alpha\" name=\"ITA\"/>||0||39||10\n|-\n|[[2007\u201308 Inter Milan season|2007\u201308]]\n|23||1||4||0||3<ref group=\"lower-alpha\" name=\"UCL\"/>||0||1<ref group=\"lower-alpha\" name=\"ITA\"/>||0||33||1\n|-\n|[[2008\u201309 Inter Milan season|2008\u201309]]\n|8||0||2||0||5<ref group=\"lower-alpha\" name=\"UCL\"/>||1||0||0||15||1\n|-\n|[[2009\u201310 Inter Milan season|2009\u201310]]\n|12||0||4||0||4<ref group=\"lower-alpha\" name=\"UCL\"/>||0||0||0||20||0\n|-\n|[[2010\u201311 Inter Milan season|2010\u201311]]\n|8||0||1||0||1<ref group=\"lower-alpha\" name=\"UCL\"/>||0||1<ref group=\"lower-alpha\" name=\"ITA\"/>||0||11||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!184!!18!!25!!0!!63!!2!!4!!0!!276!!20\n|-\n|rowspan=\"1\"|[[Chennaiyin FC|Chennaiyin]]\n|[[2014 Indian Super League season|2014]]\n|rowspan=\"1\"|[[Indian Super League]]\n|7||0||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||colspan=\"2\"|\u2014||7||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Career total\n!385!!55!!37!!1!!65!!2!!4!!0!!491!!58\n|}\n<references group=\"lower-alpha\"/>\n\n===International===\nSource:<ref>{{NFT player|id=3371|name=Marco Materazzi|accessdate=25 December 2015}}</ref><ref name=\"EU-Football.info\">{{cite web|url=https://eu-football.info/_player.php?id=13247|title=Marco Materazzi - national football team player|publisher=EU-Football.info|accessdate=14 October 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181014053224/https://eu-football.info/_player.php?id=13247|archive-date=14 October 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n{| class=wikitable style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|+ Appearances and goals by national team and year\n|-\n!National team!!Year!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=8|[[Italy national football team|Italy]]\n|2001||4||0\n|-\n|2002||5||0\n|-\n|2003||1||0\n|-\n|2004||8||0\n|-\n|2005||7||0\n|-\n|2006||10||2\n|-\n|2007||4||0\n|-\n|2008||2||0\n|-\n!colspan=2|Total!!41!!2\n|}\