razzi|accessdate=25 December 2015}}</ref><ref name=\"EU-Football.info\">{{cite web|url=https://eu-football.info/_player.php?id=13247|title=Marco Materazzi - national football team player|publisher=EU-Football.info|accessdate=14 October 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181014053224/https://eu-football.info/_player.php?id=13247|archive-date=14 October 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n{| class=wikitable style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|+ Appearances and goals by national team and year\n|-\n!National team!!Year!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=8|[[Italy national football team|Italy]]\n|2001||4||0\n|-\n|2002||5||0\n|-\n|2003||1||0\n|-\n|2004||8||0\n|-\n|2005||7||0\n|-\n|2006||10||2\n|-\n|2007||4||0\n|-\n|2008||2||0\n|-\n!colspan=2|Total!!41!!2\n|}\n\n===International goals===\n''Italy score listed first, score column indicates score after each Materazzi goal.''<ref name=\"EU-Football.info\"/>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n|+ International goals by date, venue, cap, opponent, score, result and competition\n|-\n!scope=col|No.\n!scope=col data-sort-type=date|Date\n!scope=col|Venue\n!scope=col|Cap\n!scope=col|Opponent\n!scope=col|Score\n!scope=col|Result\n!scope=col|Competition\n|-\n!scope=row|1\n|22 June 2006||[[Volksparkstadion]], [[Hamburg]], Germany||align=center|29||{{fb|CZE}}||align=center|1\u20130||align=center|2\u20130||[[2006 FIFA World Cup]] \n|-\n!scope=row|2\n|9 July 2006||[[Olympiastadion (Berlin)|Olympiastadion]], [[Berlin]], Germany||align=center|32||{{fb|FRA}}||align=center|1\u20131||align=center|1\u20131 <small>(5\u20133 [[Penalty shoot-out (association football)|p]])||[[2006 FIFA World Cup Final]]\n|}\n\n===Managerial===\nAll competitive league games (league and domestic cup) and international matches (including friendlies) are included.\n{{updated|2 December 2016}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" |Team\n! rowspan=\"2\" |Nat\n! rowspan=\"2\" |Year\n! colspan=\"5\" |Record\n|-\n!G!!W!!D!!L!!